Interface PsyArithmetic<T extends PsyArithmetic<T>>

Type Parameters:

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:

@Type("arithmetic") public interface PsyArithmetic<T extends PsyArithmetic<T>> extends PsyAdditive<T>, PsyMultiplicative<T>
The representation of arithmetic, a type of object that is an operand of arithmetic operation. This interface declares methods for multiplication, division.
